200985.name: I'm good on the front lines, too!

200988.name: Farzen, you can advance another step!

200989.name: I knew it was going to be a tough fight!

200990.name: If we can just hold out now, we've won!

200991.name: So they're ready, just as I planned.

200992.name: The demon's still up?! No, that's okay.

200993.name: It's half-dead from the last strike!

200994.name: To make it through this crisis, I'll...

200995.name: ...need my own skills, not just Weiss's.

200996.name: Weiss would scold me if he saw this.

200997.name: Farzen, you can pull back now!

200998.name: You've done a great job already!

200999.name: We can't have the leader fall, Rouche!

201000.name: I'll take over for now, so pull back!

201001.name: It's okay to play it safe, Julius!

201003.name: I've failed! I should've known it...

201006.name: I can't let anything happen to you!

201007.name: Did I go beyond mere imitation?

201009.name: I'm good on the front lines, too!

201015.name: I have never felt you were a burden.

201016.name: And you needn't worry at all.

201017.name: I told the Hall that this might happen.

201018.name: Yes, that's him. You know him, too.

201019.name: He'd run straight here if he could.

201020.name: My subjects hail me as a hero-king!

201021.name: I will not yield before any foe!

201022.name: Tighten the castle guard! Double it!

201023.name: Don't let a single foe near Mariela!

201025.name: I will keep you safe no matter what.

201033.name: Someone must know of my power, father.

201034.name: There is an army bound for us, yes?

201035.name: I never wished for these visions...

201036.name: They only make me a burden...

201038.name: The Summoners' Hall? Your friend there?

201039.name: The forces bound for our nation...

201041.name: I only want to prevent more suffering...

201042.name: I can see signs of upheaval to come...

201043.name: I only wish this was simple unease.

201053.name: I can smell it from across the Gate!

201054.name: A perfect woman's scent, and more!

201056.name: I always go out to steal new wives.

201057.name: A bad feeling? You're my daughter and...

201059.name: My nose is tingling and telling me...

201060.name: ...that my new wife's power is amazing!

201061.name: With her power, I might end up...

201064.name: She had a bad hunch about this...

201065.name: Serge's off on recon at the perimeter?

201066.name: I was right to trust him with Sonia.

201074.name: It's not like I'm really worried...

201075.name: I just have a bad feeling, is all.

201076.name: I know. Taking wives from other races...

201079.name: I'm sure I'm right, since it's you.

201081.name: I'll shut up about it. Go wild today!

201083.name: It's not an omen. And it's not like me.

201084.name: Serge... Oh, he's gone already. Typical.

201085.name: All I can do is trust dad and wait.

201094.name: Sonia, is there something bothering you?

201095.name: In Ishgria, land of the fittest...

201098.name: My skills keep me alive. They're real.

201099.name: Time to train for war with the dragons.

201100.name: He left without checking the perimeter.

201101.name: Just like Viktor, leader of the lions.

201102.name: Sonia left already? That went smoothly.

201103.name: It seems like a sign of clan trust.

201104.name: Viktor, I haven't forgotten my debt.

201115.name: Mariela?! Get back inside your room!

201118.name: How can they be so strong?!

201119.name: I will defend Mariela with my life!

201120.name: Demon scum! You won't get past me!

201135.name: Father, nobody else needs to be hurt!

201137.name: My father is suffering because of me...

201139.name: So if I go with you...

201141.name: I won't let you harm my country further.

201153.name: The dragon scum attacked with dad gone.

201154.name: Was that what my feeling was about?!

201155.name: Serge, thank you. You saw through it.

201157.name: Yeah, dad. Beat the dragons down!

201158.name: We can't let them get away with this!

201159.name: I'm from the lion clan, too. I'll win this!

201185.name: Leave Sonia to me. You go fight!

201186.name: Argh, there's so many of them...!

201187.name: I'll keep Sonia safe no matter what!

201188.name: That's the only way to repay my debt!

201190.name: Then I just need to buy her time!

201203.name: This is terrible... Those dragon scum!

201204.name: The cowards struck while I was away!

201205.name: You both fought well without me.

201206.name: Now fall back and leave the rest to me!

201207.name: So you're here to greet me, Barion?

201209.name: Argh... You came at my people like this?

201211.name: So long as my people live, I will win!

201212.name: I can't let myself lose to you!!

201213.name: Sonia... I'm sorry it ended this way.

201220.name: A dragon? Who are you people?

201231.name: Ohh... Oww... That storm was awful.

201233.name: Argh! And we just cleared the storm!

201234.name: We didn't even want to come here!

201235.name: Tsch, and the storm screwed up the ship.

201237.name: Let's fix the ship and get out of here!

201238.name: Where did that Falma get to?

201239.name: He didn't get thrown off, right?

201240.name: Whew... We finally lost the dragons.

201241.name: No need to stick around where they live.

201252.name: Where are we? I don't like this place...

201253.name: What are those? Some race of...dragons?

201254.name: Unknown foes, unknown place. Bad idea.

201255.name: We're getting out of here, Grafl!

201257.name: It's not like Grand Gaia at all...

201259.name: Grafl's doing repairs. I've got this!

201260.name: Whew... Managed to drive them off.

201261.name: We'll move once he gets the ship fixed.

201283.name: Who are you? Do you know where you are?!

201285.name: If our chief weds a human woman...

201286.name: W-Well, really, you are meant to be...

201292.name: If you say you can accept it...

201293.name: ...then I will hold my piece. Still...

201303.name: The flying ship was sighted here?

201304.name: And the ship's crew was human?

201306.name: That again? Enough! Lord Barion decided.

201307.name: You intend to disobey our leader?

201308.name: No more about that. It's over.

201309.name: And if you think she's a normal human...

201312.name: She isn't from this world, and yet...

201314.name: I do have my own opinions on this...

201315.name: ...but she will be good for Lord Barion.

201324.name: Barion's wife has had a child.

201325.name: We're all that's left of the lion clan.

201326.name: Yet he works to expand his clan...

201327.name: I will kill his child, the dragon heir!

201328.name: It's not innocent! It's his child!

201329.name: I won't forget the pain of our losses!

201331.name: For dad, and all of our clan...

201332.name: I will avenge you, one way or another!

201345.name: Huh?! Kill it? An innocent child?!

201347.name: Fine. Your father saved my life.

201348.name: So, logically, I have to serve his daughter.

201349.name: Viktor... You ordered me to protect her.

201350.name: I'm going to, no matter what comes next.

201351.name: I hate Barion and his clan, too. But...

201352.name: Don't even think it. Right now, I...

201353.name: ...will do what Sonia wants. That's all!

201364.name: The lion demons are after my child!

201365.name: And they've come so close already!

201366.name: Lyonesse, I must ask a favor.

201367.name: I entrust you with my...with our child.

201368.name: No, if you fight here, the danger is...

201369.name: That is the future I see!

201370.name: I'll hold the lions off for a while.

201371.name: Lyonesse, take my child to Grand Gaia!

201372.name: I will try to call a trusted friend.

201373.name: If you can make it to him...

201374.name: Are you the ones after my child?

201375.name: I won't let you near him!

201376.name: I can sense deep sadness from you.

201377.name: But I cannot let you pass!

201378.name: I spent my life to create that barrier.

201379.name: Now I know why I have these visions!

201380.name: I've bought enough time. Now, I...

201393.name: A vision from your powers? What was it?

201395.name: ...but we never imagined she'd do this!

201396.name: Nonsense! I can take them myself!

201399.name: Very well. I will do as you say.

201400.name: I will keep the Dragon clan's heir safe.

201401.name: Argh! When we ended the Lion clan...

201403.name: No, I...I should follow Mariela's lead.

201404.name: Move forward, don't mourn the past.

201405.name: Mariela, you were Lord Barion's wife.

201406.name: I won't let your death have been in vain!

201410.name: They're after me! So Mariela is...

201411.name: To keep Lord Barion's child safe...

201412.name: ...I must hide him. They come later.

201413.name: This will do for now... Okay.

201414.name: Now, I face them as a dragon warrior!

201415.name: Why are you so focused on this child?

201416.name: We may not be, but he's innocent!

201417.name: Urgh... I can feel their rage!

201418.name: But I won't die in vain, as a dragon!

201419.name: At last. You're the one Mariela trusted.

201430.name: I've finally found you. This is the end.

201431.name: Now you'll feel our hatred... Our rage!

201432.name: I see... You're one of their best.

201434.name: Killing both will hurt him even more!

201435.name: Nothing will change my resolve on this.

201436.name: Serge, you search for the child.

201437.name: You'll be facing me, dragon woman!

201438.name: I'll find the kid once you're dead.

201439.name: My dad was so kind to your people...

201440.name: I'm the only one left to avenge him!

201442.name: The strength to beat this dragon scum!

201443.name: Killing the child would've been empty.

201444.name: I knew that. Dad, Serge...I'm sorry...

201450.name: Watch out! She's one of Barion's elites.

201452.name: So you really will kill the child?

201453.name: Alright. Then as a lion clan member...

201456.name: I have no mercy for those who interfere!

201457.name: Such strange power. Are you dragon clan?

201458.name: Then you're just another enemy to us!

201459.name: We're isolated now, and can't turn back.

201460.name: Whether or not I'm lost, I can't turn back!

201461.name: It's for the best I couldn't find him.

201462.name: I'm sorry, Sonia... See you in hell...

201471.name: Are you the Summoners who've invaded?

201472.name: I can sense Lord Barion's presence!

201473.name: Blue hair and eyes...? C-Could he be?!

201477.name: Very well... I will take you there now.

201478.name: To see your father, Lord Barion...

201479.name: Lyonesse, the child you defended is here.

201480.name: He looks human. To awaken his power...

201481.name: I must awaken his demon blood.

201482.name: This is pitiful, for Lord Barion's son.

201483.name: I must awaken his power immediately...

201484.name: You will come to us of your own will.

201485.name: No, you will have no choice but to come!

201490.name: Ugh, now it's a dragon-looking demon...

201491.name: Just when I thought I'd shaken Shusui...

201492.name: ...I run into a demon like this.

201493.name: What's up? Why are you staring at me?

201494.name: If you won't fight, that's fine with me.

201495.name: My father?! You know my father?!

201496.name: What kind of person is he?

201497.name: I always wanted to know my real dad...

201498.name: ...but I never tried to look into him.

201499.name: Of course, I love old man Grahdens...

201500.name: ...but I still want to know my real dad.

201501.name: Can I really just kill this demon?

201502.name: And if I learn who I really am...

201510.name: You... I see. So you survived...

201511.name: It matters not whether you are my son...

201512.name: This is Ishgria. Show me your power!

201513.name: Hmph. It seems you have forgotten how...

201514.name: ...to use your power while among humans.

201517.name: Power is everything here, and if you...

201518.name: ...cannot use your power, you will die.

201519.name: Cast off your emotions, they weaken you!

201520.name: Just as they did the Lion clan's leader!

201521.name: Your eyes seem weak, but hold strength.

201522.name: I see now! You have reminded me!

201523.name: All in Ishgria hate, and are hated!

201524.name: The weak sink beneath destiny's waves!

201525.name: Use your strength, child of the dragon!

201526.name: Has humanity made you a coward?!

213951.name: I can move but...this doesn't look good!

213953.name: I guess this is it, then...

213954.name: No...I don't want to lose anything more!

213960.name: It's like I'm in a different world...

213961.name: I have people to protect...my friends...

213962.name: I have to trust their faith in me...

213963.name: I have to find a way out of here.

213975.name: Now isn't the time to lose my focus...

213976.name: I have to make sure they get out alive!

213977.name: All that matters is that they're safe!

213982.name: Lara, I have a favor to ask of you.

213983.name: I want you to part with that dragon...

213985.name: You've been together a long time, but...

213986.name: If it is what I think it is...then...

213987.name: Please. It's for your own sake...!

213989.name: That's all the more reason to...!

213990.name: That dragon may bring you misfortune...

213991.name: I don't want to lose you!

213992.name: Lara?! I guess she got away...

214002.name: Huh? Why'd she go and do that...?

214004.name: What do you mean by that?

214007.name: I don't care what you say, Felice...

214009.name: I can't bear to fight you, Felice!

214023.name: ...in the hopes of raising healthy boys.

214024.name: I wish I could get one for my son...

214025.name: I see, this is what they do in Ishgria.

214026.name: It sure is a conveniently huge fish...

214031.name: I can do this. I'll catch it myself...

214032.name: Lord Barion, do human customs amuse you?

214042.name: I've never heard of this custom...

214043.name: But can I find carp streamers here?

214044.name: Why not just use a huge fish?

214048.name: Are you telling me to catch the fish?

214050.name: Mariela, step back. I can do this!

214051.name: Lord Barion?! Th-This is for the heir...

214052.name: Liomerg, help me out, for the heir!

214061.name: What is it you wish of me...?

214062.name: What do you think you're doing...?

214112.name: I guess...it was an enemy you saw.

214113.name: Looks like an imperial scout unit...

214114.name: We've seen them. They can't escape!

214116.name: They accepted me, and you as well...

214117.name: I'll never turn my back on you!

214118.name: Power even my partner can't see?

214119.name: Argh...if it buys us some time...!

214120.name: Did you think you could escape our eyes?

214121.name: Did you think you could escape our eyes?

214122.name: Did you think you could escape our eyes?

214123.name: Did you think you could escape our eyes?

214124.name: Shion, you feel it too, don't you?

214125.name: We're under attack! Get ready for it!

214132.name: I feel magic similar to myself from you.

214133.name: Are we perhaps from the same house...?

214136.name: Ugh! Would you just listen to me?

214137.name: You call that strong? Genius? Come on!

214138.name: See? This is how you use power!!

214139.name: Surprised? You ain't seen nothing yet.

214140.name: You dare call yourself a genius?!

214142.name: It's still not enough...to beat her...!

214145.name: I've got to become stronger to beat her...

214146.name: Afraid of what I could do, were you?

214147.name: Why does she try to hide her power...?

214148.name: You want to fight? I've grown, you know!

214149.name: We're the strong ones, the chosen ones!

214150.name: Could this power be the Holy Emperor...?

214162.name: The same house? You mean our ancestors?

214163.name: I've no idea why such a person is here.

214164.name: This wimp is our ancestor? Unbelievable.

214165.name: If this person really is my ancestor...

214166.name: ...then I really must be a genius!

214167.name: Huh? Where'd you get so much power...?

214168.name: Uhh...actually I knew you were strong!

214169.name: I wanted to see my ancestors' power...

214170.name: I'm soo sorry! I really am!

214173.name: (Okay! I'll show people what I can do!)

214175.name: I am the genius conjurer of La Veda!

214176.name: Huh? What was that just now...?

214177.name: Ivris, time to begin today's training!

214178.name: Don't go falling first, my ancestors!

214181.name: The knight?! I-I'm not afraid of them!!

214182.name: Lord Will...! I will try even harder!

214183.name: Mind getting out of my way?

214185.name: Ivris isn't here? That's why she's weak!

214192.name: Sis! That's rude to our ancestors...!

214194.name: Talking like that to our ancestors...

214196.name: (Huh. I'm seeing her in a new light...)

214197.name: (Though they do seem a bit similar.)

214201.name: I thought I felt someone strong...

214202.name: (Wha? Ancestors are not a big deal...?)

214203.name: Huh? Where did Themis disappear to?

214204.name: Phew, at least now I can relax...

214205.name: Mr. Quaid? Is this an urgent call?

214206.name: Diana, isn't Mr. Quaid with you?

214208.name: Oh, Claire. Are you by yourself today?

214209.name: Colt, have you come to see me?

214210.name: Claire and Colt get along really well.

214211.name: I didn't know they were going out today.

214222.name: Licht, what are you doing here?

214223.name: Ah...that's why you came back, isn't it?

214224.name: Thanks, I owe you. But, at this rate...

214226.name: I can't be the only one left...!

214228.name: I'll find a way we can escape together!

214230.name: I've found a way out, but...but...!!

214231.name: Is it worth even sacrificing Licht...?!

214232.name: You're wounded! Please, come with us!

214235.name: Don't let Licht have acted for nothing.

214236.name: Johan! Do you really hate us so?!

214244.name: I heard we've been ordered executed...

214248.name: Right. I'll find us a way out of here.

214249.name: Here, in this land, I still need you...!

214250.name: A foreign expedition order...? A trap?

214252.name: Alessa! Hurry up and get out of here!!

214253.name: I won't let you go after Alessa...!

214254.name: This is all your doing, isn't it?!

214255.name: An emperor wouldn't likely come here...

214260.name: How are things with Regil, Azalea?

214261.name: Gotcha! Tsk, tsk, gotta stay focused!

214262.name: Haha, no need to be embarrassed.

214263.name: You can't fool me with that silly trick.

214265.name: Sorry, I just couldn't help myself.

214267.name: She must've gone to be with Regil.

214268.name: Can't be helped, I'll go it alone today.

214269.name: Can't be helped, I'm on my own...!

214280.name: Hey, Sis! Let's spar again today!

214281.name: Wh-What do you mean? I didn't...

214284.name: You're right. I'll keep trying my best!

214285.name: Geez! Don't tease me like that!

214287.name: Oh wait, I think Valen called for her.

214288.name: I'll test how far I can get on my own!

214289.name: I'll see how much I can handle myself!

214302.name: Alright... Perfect for a big job.

214303.name: Huh? Who are you? What do you mean?

214304.name: So it's not Diastima's language either?

214306.name: Get it together! The wound's not deep!

214307.name: Ahh, this is dull... What to do today?

214308.name: Huh? Oh, Ionia. Did you hear that?

214334.name: There's no way I can lose against this!

214335.name: Did you forget my power in my absence?

214336.name: I don't need your protection, but fine.

214337.name: It seems there are still enemies around.

214338.name: I'll handle this and find a way home!

214344.name: I'll find you, so hang in there, Crabby!

214345.name: I can see everyone...what is this thing?

214346.name: Melchio! You're mine, whatever it takes!

214347.name: I can tell the difference from my crab!

214374.name: So we have to continue fighting, still.

214375.name: I learned what fighting means, with her.

214376.name: The thrill, and the ultimate challenge!

214377.name: If I could return to that time again...

214378.name: I would grow even stronger than now!

214381.name: It feels like I missed another chance...

214382.name: Hehe, it's odd. I think she's friendly.

214394.name: They're gonna want more in the future...

214396.name: You want a whole lot more red, huh?

214398.name: Oh, by the way, what survey?

214399.name: If you wanted it all red so badly...

214402.name: All good things must come to an end...

214411.name: Ah, the rainy season has come...

214412.name: It's not great for the flowers, but...

214417.name: But my hair can't take the humidity!

214418.name: Ugh, my hair is a mess again...

214419.name: This time of year is terrible for it.

214421.name: My hair is all over the place!

214423.name: I just don't know what to do with it!

214424.name: If it weren't for this humidity...

214425.name: Wait, aren't you a Water type...?

214427.name: Water is vital to life, yes.

214429.name: My hair is torture this time of year.

214430.name: Both gods and humans suffer bad hair.

214442.name: I know. Oh, I know that feeling well.

214443.name: As the great Lord Lucius's disciple...

214446.name: In order to be the perfect disciple...

214447.name: ...I need my hair to be perfect!

214448.name: But this humidity! My beautiful hair!

214451.name: Why does this humidity defy me?!

214454.name: If only there were no humidity at all!

214455.name: L-Lord Lucius! This, ah, major issue...

214456.name: Lord Lucius! To serve you as disciple...

214457.name: B-But, Lord Lucius! I haven't forgotten!

214463.name: Ahaha, I can look like this, too!

214464.name: I do feel like it's kinda ugly, though.

214465.name: Now! Let's go fulfill our objective.

214466.name: How shall I fight you, hmm...?

214467.name: Goodness, you hurt me in this form!

214470.name: You really are a child of chaos!

214471.name: At this rate, my destiny is...

214473.name: This is great! I'm having so much fun!

214474.name: I sure hope it lasts to the end!

214483.name: How do you think you got big, anyway?!

214484.name: Oh, yeah?! Say that to my face!

214485.name: Shut up! Takes one to know one, idiot!

214486.name: What?! Your family raised you that way?!

214488.name: I can't admit I ate Sonia's snacks.

214489.name: I've got to solve this right now...

214490.name: She'll want them back with interest.

214491.name: W-Wait! Sonia! I-It was my fault!

214492.name: She left... I've got to grow up.

214502.name: Dad! You ate my snacks, didn't you?!

214503.name: Is not! Pay me back, with interest!

214504.name: What, you think you get credit, idiot?!

214505.name: Yeah, I said it! You're an idiot!

214506.name: Only idiots are childish like you!

214509.name: I bet dad did this! Where is he?!

214510.name: Oh, whatever. I'll get interest on it...

214511.name: Dad, did you just run away?!

214512.name: Fine, you get away with it this time.

214522.name: In this world where strength prevails...

214524.name: We have not yielded our dreams yet.

214526.name: None may say what awaits you.

214527.name: Some day you will understand, as well.

214528.name: You will. Your life is just beginning.

214529.name: Yes, just living alongside loved ones...

214530.name: Mora, our hope lies in you.

214531.name: Our dream is not yet done.

214532.name: We have hope. Hope for your future!

214542.name: How do you feel, about this world?

214543.name: What do you want for this world, Mora?

214544.name: You are our new hope, and our dream...

214545.name: You decide how your future will grow.

214546.name: A fascinating chance meeting changed me.

214547.name: Yes, life is full of strange turns.

214548.name: Precisely. Many new meetings await you.

214549.name: Even this world can be beautiful.

214551.name: Indeed... I look forward to her growth.

214553.name: Let's put our faith in her future.

214562.name: I'm quite disgusted by this conflict.

214563.name: I want to end this senseless violence!

214564.name: I will make that dream a reality.

214567.name: Does something like that await me, then?

214568.name: Hehe, I'm happy we had this talk.

214569.name: Let's treasure this happy time together.

214570.name: Thank you. As I will for your dream.

214571.name: I will end this senseless violence!

214580.name: Hm? You're swordsmen, too, are you?

214581.name: Want to shoot the breeze, then?

214583.name: It's too hot to touch, you know?

214584.name: You got asked to do that?!

214585.name: Surely you could've blown up over that.

214586.name: I guess we all have our struggles...

214587.name: But we've just got to do it!

214588.name: Our swords are trusted partners, right?

214589.name: We have to treat them right!

214601.name: Sure, that might bring back memories.

214603.name: Why not chat for a bit?

214604.name: Speaking of which, the other day...

214605.name: I got asked to grill some meat this way.

214607.name: True, I'm not suited to cooking...

214609.name: They're an issue if I forget what I hit.

214612.name: That was a good thing to do.

214620.name: It was time for a break anyway.

214621.name: I'd love to join and have people around.

214622.name: This heat fires my sword up like mad.

214623.name: All right, this is the place to rest.

214624.name: The sword's shape is fine for combat...

214625.name: But what do I do with it when I sleep?

214627.name: Doesn't that make people look great?

214628.name: I thought just fighting was enough.

214629.name: Swords are always with us, after all.

214631.name: That's tripping me up, a bit.

214633.name: I don't even want another sword now!

214634.name: A partner? I'm not so sure about that...

214636.name: I'll be counting on you, partner!

214637.name: Yeah, this was a good idea.

214638.name: I appreciate it too. I had a nice break.

214639.name: It can be a pain, but...

2127283.name: (I can't tell them I want shaved ice...)

2127301.name: I sense powerful spirits from you all...

2127302.name: Please, grant me just one match!

2127305.name: I'll respond with a secret technique!

2127309.name: That little tap took you down? Sad...

2127310.name: Silly me, I was expecting more from you.

2127311.name: Can't be helped. Guess I'll train you!

2127313.name: As a reward for making it this far...

2127314.name: Allow me to show you my spear skills!

2127330.name: How are you feeling today, Hisui?

2127331.name: I promise not to hold back...

2127332.name: So come at me with all you've got!

2127335.name: But I won't let myself lose!

2127336.name: I just shrugged off your final attack!

2127340.name: I will carry on your spirit, all of it!

2127341.name: And burn "the strongest" into my being!

2127351.name: I don't have much time left...

2127352.name: This is probably my last battle...

2127354.name: But I can still see doubt in your moves.

2127355.name: If you're not serious...I will be!

2127356.name: Ha ha, with pure power as your style...

2127381.name: But I have a secret left...

2127390.name: It's not over yet! This place...is mine.

2127401.name: Then I get to do what I want!

2127403.name: I'll protect many people for you, mom.

2127405.name: Dad! Say what you will, I'm going!

2127406.name: I can't ignore people who need my help!

2127407.name: You can't stop me from going!

2127408.name: It's what I decided for myself!

2127422.name: I shouldn't worry about Lucana now.

2127423.name: I've got to think of Limera and Rouche.

2127425.name: I believe you can do it!

2127427.name: People you can't save when in a group...

2127430.name: I think you know what we wanted.

2127442.name: I can't believe Limera would leave...

2127443.name: I have to follow my sister and help...

2127449.name: I know how you both must feel.

2127461.name: ...that you'll come back even if you go.

2127463.name: Just be sure to come back...

2127466.name: Limera, we want to save people too...

2127467.name: But that will only lead to more sadness.

2127468.name: Both of you, be sure to come back!

2127470.name: Necromancy has a bad image, right?

2127471.name: But it's not like that at all, actually.

2127472.name: We'll show you how amazing it is.

2127479.name: Yes! You can even control your own soul!

2127480.name: To protect someone even in death...

2127481.name: If you feel that way, you should learn.

2127483.name: I still have so much to talk about!

2127484.name: Sorry, stick around a bit longer?

2127486.name: You're a bit better than the dead...

2127487.name: Don't get mad! I was kidding!

2127489.name: Am I in big trouble now?

2127492.name: I haven't had this much fun in years!

2127495.name: Death isn't a barrier to necromancy.

2127498.name: Someone even more immersed than us!

2127499.name: Show me the fruits of your research!

2127502.name: Then there might be more necromancers...

2127503.name: That went better than I expected.

2127506.name: That time was a lot more fun.

2127507.name: Real fights are better than research!

2127509.name: Gotta get serious now or I'll lose...

2127521.name: You can learn where souls go with this.

2127523.name: That is the root of all necromancy.

2127524.name: The art of peering into the abyss...

2127525.name: It can defy the laws of life and death.

2127527.name: Magic to transcend the bounds of death.

2127531.name: You get a special one-on-one lesson.

2127533.name: Rather than Summoning, you might be...

2127536.name: Do you mind if I check out your soul?

2127537.name: You could even give it to me, maybe?

2127539.name: With you, I might be able to see...

2127540.name: Will you look into the abyss with us?

2127542.name: If I had your power, it would be easy...

2127545.name: How many souls must I consume...

2127548.name: I wonder how much your soul is worth?

2127549.name: Not quite what I had hoped for...

2127550.name: Perhaps everything falls to the abyss...

2127552.name: With you, I could make it there...

2127560.name: Weary as I am from battle...

2127561.name: I can't save people like this...

2127562.name: Master, will you save them in my place?

2127563.name: It seems I have dishonored my name...

2127564.name: I return the name "Zelban" to you...

2127565.name: So please, go in my place!

2127567.name: I will share the things you taught me!

2127569.name: The La Veda fencing master taught me...

2127573.name: I can still wield this much power...

2127578.name: Someone like this is a surprise.

2127579.name: I still have far to go on my path...

2127581.name: It's time to teach you a lesson again!

2127587.name: Fall to the La Vedan style!

2127589.name: Why do you have that sword?!

2127591.name: Taste this secret La Vedan technique!

2127594.name: I am indeed the strongest Zelban!

2127601.name: It's because you use your power...

2127604.name: I have no desire for that name.

2127605.name: Go, and pass down your title and skill.

2127607.name: Maybe I was attached to it, once.

2127611.name: I have devoted my life to the sword...

2127612.name: ...so show me you can take this!

2127614.name: This might be fun, for a change!

2127617.name: Have you trained more since then?

2127618.name: I will put you to the test!

2127619.name: Well, you seem to have gotten better.

2127620.name: But I'm not done fighting yet!

2127621.name: You might be worthy of the name Zelban.

2127622.name: So you're the one my student chose...

2127623.name: Allow me to put you to the test!

2127628.name: I seem to have gotten a good student.

2127632.name: So this is the current Zelban...

2127633.name: Been awhile since I felt this excited!

2127634.name: Show me you can take this!

2127636.name: This might be fun, for a change!

2127652.name: When it comes to cold weather...

2127654.name: Huh? Cold weather is for reading?

2127655.name: That doesn't fill me up, so no.

2127672.name: And when it comes to cold weather...

2127673.name: The cold is for making art.

2127676.name: I can't let that statement slide...

2127690.name: Everyone, when it comes to cold weather...

2127693.name: Cold weather is all about reading!

2127694.name: Spring is for reading! And summer!

2127695.name: And fall, and winter too! Got it?!

2127696.name: Lancia, when it comes to cold weather...

2127697.name: Soleil, when it comes to the cold...

2127698.name: When it comes to cold weather...!

2127703.name: I just wanted to talk about the cold...

2127710.name: What brings you all to me?

2127711.name: All of you...you're all so irritating...

2127717.name: Fine, I'll play with you a bit more.

2127730.name: You don't seem like you're having fun...

2127731.name: If you want...I could play with you?

2127732.name: Sorry, but I might break you...

2127735.name: If you don't...I'll break you first!

2127737.name: I can tell you really want to break me.

2127740.name: I had just started to really enjoy it...

2127751.name: Aaron... I've been given the power to seal.

2127752.name: Your great powers will kill you.

2127753.name: Aaron... I shall seal away your power.

2127754.name: There is nothing left to say...

2127755.name: Do not attempt to fight back.

2127757.name: That is not true power. Seek real strength.

2127761.name: I've become stronger than you, brother.

2127764.name: Urgh... Our powers differ so greatly...

2127767.name: I will not go without a fight...!

2127770.name: Stop treating me like a child!

2127771.name: Me and this precious little one...

2127772.name: We'll get stronger together! You'll see!

2127775.name: Are you also trying to split us up?!

2127780.name: And I'll finally be of use to that person!

2127790.name: Diana! I found a beautiful flower!

2127796.name: Did I just say a monster was beautiful?!

2127800.name: There's no time to admire the scenery.

2127803.name: So that flower was a monster...

2127810.name: Quaid, is that really a flower?

2127811.name: I didn't say a thing! It was that flower!

2127812.name: Are you blind? It's a monster!

2127813.name: (All we've been doing is fighting here...)

2127814.name: (I just wanted to spend some time together.)

2127816.name: Quaid... Who cares about the flowers...

2127817.name: I wanted you to look at me...

2127821.name: It looks like I've found some food...

2127822.name: Satisfy my hunger as my nourishment!

2127836.name: Looks like the soup stock is about ready...

2127871.name: The flowers' miasma...is changing my body...

2127872.name: Argh... We still have enemies here...

2127873.name: I will never relinquish this land to you!

2127874.name: I will realize Lord Lucius's ambitions.

2127875.name: Urgh... The miasma is getting to me...

2127876.name: To weaken me with this poison...

2127877.name: I will lose at this rate...

2127890.name: But even if my body changes...

2127891.name: Those who oppose the great Lucius...

2127892.name: Shall be buried by his loyal servant: me.

2127900.name: No... Father only tried to protect me...

2127911.name: We don't know when he'll strike...

2127912.name: I will not give my daughter to a ruffian like you!

2127913.name: I will give my life to protect Mariela!

2127914.name: That is my duty as your father!

2127918.name: That brute will never have my daughter...

2127930.name: That woman has the gift of the sight...

2127932.name: I can't wait any more time here!

2127934.name: I have to exterminate the dragon demons!

2127935.name: I'll finish this with my next move.

2127943.name: Everyone is so into their costumes!

2127944.name: That's not a prank! It's a crime...

2127946.name: Dressing up in costumes isn't an everyday thing!

2127947.name: Apparently people dressed up during festivals...

2127949.name: I think the owner of that store is angry!

2127952.name: Coming to the aid of those in need!

2127962.name: We should have a costume party!

2127966.name: You're just as wise as the real Elimo!

2127967.name: That Zelnite that was stealing before...

2127968.name: Thieves sure are quick to escape...

2127969.name: Wait! Where did that Elimo go?!

2127980.name: Zelnite is the best Unit to cosplay as!

2127981.name: And as the convincing Zelnite that I am...

2127982.name: I'm gonna steal all your candy and snacks!

2127985.name: I can only get away with this today!

2128003.name: You're in the way. I'll end you myself.

2128006.name: Now, how to end Holia with you lot...

2128010.name: Hah, well then, I'll just end you here!

2128013.name: I'll just keep you from moving!

2128015.name: How is it? I bet it hurts!

2128016.name: Now I'll take my time working on you.

2128019.name: Then I'll just shut you down by force!

2128031.name: I will kill you all here.

2128032.name: What an odd technique that was...

2128035.name: I will slay any foe in one strike!

2128039.name: My mission...is to protect the chief.

2128042.name: I'm not letting any of you leave alive!

2128053.name: All is going according to plan.

2128056.name: Oh, so the plan is progressing?

2128063.name: (Surely not a new one of Afla Dilith's?)

2128066.name: And just who in the world are you?!

2128069.name: Where should I go in this situation?

2128070.name: All I could do was restore your power...

2128081.name: A grudge against the dragon clan...

2128083.name: I won't lose so long as you serve them!

2128084.name: Don't compare me with my baby brother.

2128086.name: You're brave, doing that to my brother.

2128087.name: I will end the lion clan, I swear it!

2128088.name: You... You're in the lion clan!

2128100.name: I won't forgive attacks on my family.

2128101.name: I will kill you for our chief.

2128102.name: This isn't the limit of my power!

2128103.name: Argh, can a human be so strong?

2128104.name: Argh, can the lion clan be so strong?

2128105.name: But the chief is counting on me...

2128106.name: I can't let it all end here!

2128108.name: Don't underestimate my clan, idiot lion!

2128109.name: You're the one who killed my sister...

2128111.name: I will finish your entire clan here!

2128112.name: A whole pile of dragon clan enemies...

2128123.name: Hmph, even if we have different goals...

2128127.name: (So the next one will be even stronger.)

2128143.name: And everyone's attacking on their own...

2128151.name: Huh? It's okay to attack already?

2128152.name: This was annoying so it better hurt!

2128161.name: I'm weak... I caught a cold.

2128164.name: Huh? I feel better! I'm not coughing!

2128166.name: I should've gotten a mask from that guy.

2128167.name: Oh, did the fairy leave already?

2128172.name: Oh, my. One of them looks sick.

2128174.name: Wear a mask when it's cold out...

2128176.name: And be sure to wash your hands!

2128178.name: Once I healed them, they vanished.

2128181.name: Wear a mask like I do.

2128182.name: It goes around at this time of year.

2128184.name: Some spirits around here heal sickness.

2128185.name: They appear when an illness gets bad.

2128187.name: (How strange... I even wore a mask.)

2128189.name: There's a flu going around lately.

2128190.name: I hear it spreads when people cough.

2128192.name: I'll be fine wearing a mask.

2128200.name: The year's over. Did Limera get home?

2128202.name: I need to plan future training.

2128203.name: That will help protect more people!

2128204.name: I've got to work hard as the leader...

2128205.name: And I have to make rules for the troops.

2128206.name: They all act on their own...

2128207.name: I bet my mom and dad are worried.

2128208.name: I never knew leading was so hard.

2128210.name: I've still got people to keep safe!

2128212.name: Mom and dad are waiting for you!

2128213.name: I'll cover your work over New Years.

2128215.name: I'll be there as soon as this is done!

2128217.name: It's all right! I have time still, but...

2128218.name: I'll be sure to make it!

2128233.name: But I can do the most damage!

2128234.name: Fine, then I'll prove how strong I am!

2128236.name: I can still hit even harder, too!

2200555.name: I'll always win, no matter what!

2200558.name: I'm always up for a challenge!

21102400.name: I won't go down easy either!

21103400.name: Well, let me show mine too.

21104200.name: I know this one, I guess...

21105600.name: Follow the will of the gods!

21106400.name: Guess I can get serious now.

21107400.name: Will you fight to the end?!

21109300.name: Should I give it my all?

21110200.name: How do you like my dancing?

21113800.name: Alone in the end after all.

21114400.name: Shut up! I'll do it my way!

21118100.name: My gun never misses a shot.

21118300.name: I'll go on without a shield.

21125800.name: Fine, but help me out here.

21126700.name: I think you may be senile.

21127400.name: Are you getting up on time?

21129700.name: I don't wanna be a bother!

21130400.name: You may be okay, I guess...

21130600.name: I guess I should use this...

21131900.name: I'll heal you all! Hang on!

21132100.name: You won't get away with it!

21133100.name: My fire burns only my foes!

21140300.name: Is there nothing I can do?

21141100.name: Yes love? Wait, it's a guy?!

21141200.name: Yah! I fight for the ladies!

21141300.name: All my love is for my girls!

21141500.name: My power is for the ladies!

21142200.name: You got a problem with that?

21143300.name: I care for god nor man!

21143600.name: I'll turn it all to ashes!!!

21143700.name: Only I shall end it all!

21146600.name: Wait, did I it mess up?

21146900.name: That hurts! What did I do?!

21147300.name: Get away from me, you perv!!

21148300.name: I'm way too much for you!

21148700.name: Can't lose till I beat him!

21149400.name: No, I am! So shut up!!

21149500.name: Imma sear it into your head!

21151200.name: Oh, guess it's a solo now.

21152400.name: I can't sing just like that.

21152600.name: I don't wanna be a singer.

21157300.name: I'll guide it all to ruin...

21165900.name: Hah, like you have to ask...

21181700.name: I'm so happy. He he he.

21182300.name: I want to chat some more...

21185100.name: I lost all to that dragon!

21189300.name: Death has taken him from me.

21189400.name: Misery is all I have left...

21189800.name: I want to see him once more.

21190600.name: It's my sole way to atone...

21191400.name: I might find a gift here.

21192000.name: No, a Cure might be best.

21192700.name: No way I can outdo her...

21196400.name: What do you plan to do?!

21201200.name: Huh?! I won't give you this!

21202000.name: I can't focus on the battle!

21202300.name: Oh, I'll get my hands on it.

21202500.name: Outta my way! I'll bash you!

21205300.name: In that case I'll join too!

21206100.name: I've no wish to play games.

21206200.name: Want to fight the God Army?

21211400.name: I won't be angry or sad!

21211500.name: I'll give it a shot too!

21211700.name: I won't be of any use...

21212100.name: Yeah, I know how you feel...

21212300.name: I can't do a thing, yet...

21212500.name: Then I shall try my best!

21213300.name: The filth is not gone yet...

21225700.name: Your art is not what I seek.

21225900.name: I walk the path of war.

21226400.name: But it's time to end it now.

21227300.name: You should stand for it too!

21232200.name: I knew this was the best!
